data.text:
Welcome to Lebold-Smith Funeral Home in Bolivar, OH

After losing a loved one, you can trust the funeral directors at Lebold-Smith Funeral Home to help you celebrate your loved one’s life. Our staff has experience planning a variety of funeral services and can assist your family in honoring your loved one no matter your personal preference, budget, culture, or religion. We pride ourselves on serving the Bolivar community and surrounding areas with compassion, dignity, and respect.
